ad.year<-function(x){as.yearmon(paste(substr(as.character(x),1,4),substr(as.character(x),6,7),sep='-'))}
p$V1<-unlist(p$V1 %>% map(ad.year))
p=arrange(p,V1)
myPMI<-function(b)
{
  m<-dlmModReg(p$V2,FALSE,dW=b[1]^2,m0=50)
  m$JFF<-matrix(0,nr=1,nc=1)
  return(m)
}
fit<-dlmMLE(p$V2,parm=0.1,build=myPMI)
mod<-myPMI(fit$par)
filted<-dlmFilter(p$V2,mod)
plot(cbind(p$V1,filted$m[-1]),col=c('black','red'),xlab='',ylab='PMI')

\(\frac{W}{V}=0.5\)

  1. \(\theta_{t-1}\) \((\theta_{t-1}|D_{t-1})\sim N(m_{t-1},C_{t-1})\)
  2. \(\theta_{t}\) \((\theta_t|D_{t-1})\sim N(m_{t-1},R_t)\)\(R_t = C_{t-1}+W_t\)
  3. 1 \((Y_t|D_{t-1})\sim N(f_t,Q_t)\)\(f_t = m_{t-1}\),\(Q_t=R_t + V_t\)
  4. \(\theta_t\) \((\theta_t|D_t)\sim N(m_t,C_t)\)\(m_t = m_{t-1} + A_t e_t\),\(C_t = A_tV_t\),\(A_t = R_t/Q_t\)\(e_t=Y_t-f_t\)
\[ (Y_t|\theta_t,D_{t-1})\sim N(\theta_t,V_t) \\ (\theta_t|D_{t-1})\sim N(m_{t-1},R_t) \] \(D_t = \{ Y_t,D_{t-1}\}\) \[ p(y_t|\theta_t,D_{t-1})=\frac{p(y_t,\theta_t,D_{t-1})}{p(\theta_t,D_{t-1})}=\frac{p(\theta_t,D_{t})}{p(D_{t-1})p(\theta_t|D_{t-1})}=\frac{p(\theta_t|D_t)p(D_t)}{p(D_{t-1})p(\theta_t|D_{t-1})} \] \[ p(\theta_t|D_t)=\frac{p(\theta_t|D_{t-1})p(y_t|\theta_t,D_{t-1})}{p(D_t)/p(D_{t-1})}=\frac{p(\theta_t|D_{t-1})p(y_t|\theta_t,D_{t-1})}{p(y_t|D_{t-1})} \] \(\theta_t\) \[ p(\theta_t|D_t)\propto p(\theta_t|D_{t-1})p(y_t|\theta_t,D_{t-1})\propto \exp[-(\theta_t-m_{t-1})^2/(2R_t) - (y_t-\theta_t)^2/(2V_t)] \] \[\begin{eqnarray*} 2\ln(p(\theta_t|D_t))&=&k_1 -(\theta_t - m_{t-1})^2R_t^{-1}-(y_t-\theta_t)^2V_t^{-1} \\ &=&k_2 -(R_t^{-1}+V_t^{-1})\theta_t^2+2(R_t^{-1}m_{t-1}+V_t^{-1}y_t)\theta_t \\ &=&k_3 -(\theta_t-m_t)^2C_t^{-1} \end{eqnarray*}\] \[\begin{eqnarray*} C_t &=& 1/[R_t^{-1}+V_t^{-1}]=R_tV_t/Q_t = A_tV_t \\ m_t &=& (R_t^{-1}m_{t-1}+y_tV_t^{-1})C_t = m_{t-1}A_tV_t/R_t+A_ty_t=m_{t-1} +A_t(y_t-m_{t-1}) =m_{t-1}+A_te_t=A_ty_t + (1-A_t)m_{t-1} \end{eqnarray*}\] \[\begin{eqnarray*} Q_t &=& R_t + V_t \\ R_t &=& C_{t-1} + W_t \\ A_t &=& \frac{R_t}{Q_t}=\frac{R_t}{R_t + V_t} \end{eqnarray*}\]

mymod<-function(b)
{
  m<-dlmModReg(x, TRUE, dV = b[1]^2,dW=c(b[2]^2,b[3]^2),
                          m0 = c(0,1))
  m$JFF<-matrix(c(0,1),nr=1,nc=2)
  return(m)
}
fit <- dlmMLE(y, parm = c(0.1, 0.01,0.02),
              build = mymod)
mod<-mymod(fit$par)
filted<-dlmFilter(y,mod)
smooth<-dlmSmooth(y,mod)
data$f<-filted$f
data$s<-smooth$s[-1,1]+smooth$s[-1,2]*x
data$date<-as.Date(rownames(data))
d=data[,2:5]
d=melt(d,id.vars='date')
